OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FThe US government is facing backlash
OL,7,Fafter posting meme-style TikTok videos
OL,8,Fof missile attacks against Iran.
OL,10,FThe videos drew criticism on social
OL,11,Fmedia, though others praised the
OL,12,Fediting. One video about the ongoing
OL,13,Fwar used the song Blow by Kesha as the
OL,14,Fbacking track.
OL,16,FShe responded on Monday, calling
OL,17,FPresident Donald Trump a "criminal
OL,18,Fpredator," and saying the post showed
OL,19,Fa "blatant disregard for human life."
OL,20,FThe audio has since been removed from
OL,21,Fthe video.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
