PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FAnother post used a killstreak
OL,7,Fanimation from the video game Call of
OL,8,FDuty.
OL,10,FChance Glasco, the founding developer
OL,11,Fof the franchise, said on X that it
OL,12,Fdidn't surprise him, revealing that
OL,13,Fthe team had previously faced pressure
OL,14,Fto make a COD game centred on Iran
OL,15,Fattacking Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FHe said: "This doesn't surprise me. I
OL,7,Fremember after Activision took over
OL,8,Fpost-Respawn formation there was a
OL,9,Fvery awkward pressure from Activision
OL,10,Ffor us to make the next CoD about Iran
OL,11,Fattacking Israel.
OL,13,F"Luckily the vast majority of our devs
OL,14,Fwere disgusted by the idea and it got
OL,15,Fshot down."
OL,17,FThe posts are receiving criticism as
OL,18,Fthe ongoing military strikes carried
OL,19,Fout by Israel and the US have resulted
OL,20,Fin the deaths of at least 1,230 people
OL,21,Fin Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
