PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FKristyan Benedict, Amnesty
OL,7,FInternational UK's Crisis Response
OL,8,FManager, said: "Some governments,
OL,9,Fparticularly the US and Israel, are
OL,10,Fdeliberately glamorising their
OL,11,Fmilitary attacks in Iran through
OL,12,Fcrass, attention-seeking content in
OL,13,Fwhat is an unmistakeable strategy of
OL,14,Fdesensitisation to violence and
OL,15,Fdehumanisation of the victims.
OL,17,F"It is as dangerous as it is
OL,18,Fcontemptible."
OL,26,@pD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
