PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FAnd this is not the first time the
OL,7,FWhite House has used meme culture for
OL,8,Fcontroversial content.
OL,10,FLast year, they faced similar backlash
OL,11,Fafter posting a video appearing to
OL,12,Fcelebrate ICE deportation operations,
OL,13,Fset to the Jet2 holiday viral TikTok
OL,14,Fsound.
OL,16,FSinger Jess Glynne, whose song is
OL,17,Ffeatured in the ad, responded, saying
OL,18,Fthe video "honestly makes her sick".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
