PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FWhile the White House has not appeared
OL,7,Fto comment on this specific clip, it
OL,8,Fhas previously responded to wider
OL,9,Fcriticisms of its social media
OL,10,Fstrategy, which includes the use of AI
OL,11,Fgenerated images, trolling and memes.
OL,13,F"Nowhere in the Constitution does it
OL,14,Fsay we can't post banger memes," it
OL,15,Fwrote on its X account in July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
