OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FMore recently, the Pokemon Company
OL,7,Fresponded to a post by the official
OL,8,FWhite House account posted on
OL,9,FThursday, which shows an aerial view
OL,10,Fof one of the franchise's Nintendo
OL,11,FSwitch games with the message: "Make
OL,12,FAmerica Great Again."
OL,14,FIn a statement to the New York Times,
OL,15,Fa company spokeswoman said: "We are
OL,16,Faware of recent social content that
OL,17,Fincludes imagery associated with our
OL,18,Fbrand.
OL,26,@nD@WrrwD@]OU
