OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,F"We were not involved in its creation
OL,7,For distribution, and no permission was
OL,8,Fgranted for the use of our
OL,9,Fintellectual property. Our mission is
OL,10,Fto bring the world together, and that
OL,11,Fmission is not affiliated with any
OL,12,Fpolitical viewpoint or agenda."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
