OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News' North American
OL,7,Fpartner in August, Trump loyalist and
OL,8,FX Strategies CEO Alex Bruesewitz
OL,9,Fexplained what he thought the White
OL,10,FHouse is hoping to achieve with its
OL,11,Fmeme and internet culture-based
OL,12,Fstrategy.
OL,14,F"He changed the game in how you
OL,15,Fcommunicate as president. And he's
OL,16,Fmore transparent, he's more direct,"
OL,17,FBruesewitz said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,F"His communication style is also more
OL,7,Fin touch with the rest of the country.
OL,8,FHe doesn't sit there behind a podium
OL,9,Fand pander and just read a script.
OL,11,F"He never fails to let the American
OL,12,Fpeople know what he's thinking,
OL,13,Fexactly how he's thinking. And he has
OL,14,Fsuch a unique communication style, and
OL,15,FI think the White House complements it
OL,16,Fwell."
OL,18,FHowever, another source familiar with
OL,19,FTrump's first-term operation said the
OL,20,Fstrategy is not without its
OL,21,Flimitations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
