PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772935393
OL,3,CWhite House faces backlash over meme-
OL,4,Cstyle videos of missile attacks on Iran
OL,6,F"I think the current strategy is
OL,7,Feffective in the sense of quick
OL,8,Fengagement, but the moment dies fast
OL,9,Fbecause it's reactionary to what the
OL,10,Fcurrent trend is," they said.
OL,12,F"My concern is not properly
OL,13,Fhighlighting the policy wins because
OL,14,Fthe feed is bogged down with too many
OL,15,Fless-serious posts."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
